possible without computers? Absolutely not. The 
thing that made a consolidation down there

17:12.461 --> 17:18.948
possible are two things, three things. Good air 
transportation, good computer tied-in systems,

17:20.290 --> 17:26.957
and good communication systems. In fact, we don't 
have the best communication system down there.

