We've got a Navy communication system, and right 
now there's a lot better commercial

17:34.718 --> 17:42.207
communication, television, satellite systems 
for command and control available other than the

17:34.718 --> 17:42.207
kind the Navy has. And I'm looking forward to maybe 
getting one of those because I think that if you're

